spec_data.Name: gdk-pixbuf2-xlib
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the old libgdk-pixbuf-xlib library that is needed by some
programs to load GdkPixbuf using bare XLib calls.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 06 Oct 2017 04:40:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Additional library for using gdk-pixbuf with bare xlib
